{"tid":1098000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轟沙中線報告偏頗  為港鐵禮頓開脫　港大專家：唔會搭沙中線","createTime":"2019-04-08T17:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T04:03:13.000Z","uid":41818,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03e37ce0c8c7d01ca49e693eb2a75d2b3feddc22","tid":1098000,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190330/photo/bkn-20190330163619672-0330_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190330163619672-0330_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=489fab21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府早前公布港鐵沙中線獨立調查委員會中期報告，中科專家證人、香港大學土木工程系副教授楊德忠形容初看報告時已「感到突然」，因內容十分偏頗，用盡語言藝術為港鐵及禮頓開脫。他質疑報告大量引用特定兩三名專家證人的證供，卻無解釋不採納他及其他專家的原因，與法庭做法不一，更表示沙中線通車後自己或不會乘搭：「真係會驚，我諗我會揸車」。<br />\n<br />\n楊指出，報告提及「專家一致同意建造細節經改動後，車站結構不會有問題」，澄清當時專家是一致同意需要經詳細檢查，但一般而言結構不會有問題，批評報告把他對一般情況的看法當成針對今次事件的意見。他又批評報告在所有調查、測試及檢驗仍未完成時，即表示結構安全是太武斷。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，報告稱工人多次將較多螺紋的B款鋼筋剪成較少螺紋的A款，並解釋只要能扭入螺絲帽就不構成安全風險。他認為說法不合邏輯，因B款造價較A款貴1倍，即使用B款代替A款，亦不需要剪掉多餘部分，「因為會更難扭」。<br />\n<br />\n他又多次批評報告不公平，更質疑被採納意見專家的資歷及經驗，「其他專家咁都話安全，真係好唔尊重事實」。他又反問：「市民睇到份咁嘅報告，佢哋會唔會覺得真係安全？」問及中科及他會否有份出席下一輪聆訊，楊指雙方至今都未收到任何通知。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190330/bkn-20190330163619672-0330_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028810746381ccb01465d4f20e11a2b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190330%2Fbkn-20190330163619672-0330_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D4028810746381ccb01465d4f20e11a2b&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=aff4bf1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190330/bkn-20190330163619672-0330_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028810746381ccb01465d4f20e11a2b</a>"},{"pid":"e37803bdebb6f2dca248378d2da4a5d89e41d2ac","tid":1098000,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T00:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />豆腐工程"},{"pid":"d832ab43c42202fd9a43c8972d257b8446515b9f","tid":1098000,"uid":229183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T00:17:03.000Z","msg":"中國工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e0c7036899c30f73d75a3be6af062976f27e51","tid":1098000,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"進步工程名單內既人仲份中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebc34222928189c915914fda429c9b4c93f4a47","tid":1098000,"uid":21398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"當年高鐵都話滲水，港珠澳大橋又話品質問題<br />\n最後咪個個湧住去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇死沙中線一開，大把香港人衝去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後港鐵賺到笑，馬時亨過幾年出黎邀功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb425df761077e8e7bde42dfc78360a57779b24","tid":1098000,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T00:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103f9f55337f8282b98bce9df735752728482f26","tid":1098000,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ebc34222928189c915914fda429c9b4c93f4a47","tid":1098000,"uid":21398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"當年高鐵都話滲水，港珠澳大橋又話品質問題<br />\n最後咪個個湧住去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇死沙中線一開，大把香港人衝去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後港鐵賺到笑，馬時亨過幾年出黎邀功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:06:19.000Z","msg":"沙中線本來就係利民基建"},{"pid":"501c9489c68d6507223e91d96d65351643f490cb","tid":1098000,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thb.gov.hk/tc/psp/publications/transport/studies/Interim%20Report%20No.1%20(Chi).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpsp%2Fpublications%2Ftransport%2Fstudies%2FInterim%2520Report%2520No.1%2520%28Chi%29.pdf&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=1ffaeb4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thb.gov.hk/tc/psp/publications/transport/studies/Interim%20Report%20No.1%20(Chi).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n其實份報告寫得好淺白，非工程底既人都睇得明<br />\n<br />\n如果認真睇完既人，相信都會認同佢地既結論"}]}